txt_1: Dave is very engaging.  The way he makes students laugh makes a lot of the more difficult material more approachable.

txt_1: Very good at explaining things, did a great job of providing examples during lectures to make content more easily understandable.  Made lots of jokes, which maintained a good atmosphere.

txt_3: Pace of material was inconsistent.  First month was too slow and easy, while at the end was many times faster.  This is reflected in class average on assignments.
txt_5: Class size was good, as was the classroom setting.  Wouldn't have been nearly as effective a learning atmosphere if it was in a lecture hall.
